wra03a-subtext: He interactive dashboard hmang hian open-ended response maktaduai 1.2 te chu hmu thei la, hei hi hmeichhia leh hmeichhe naupang aw leh digital analysis-a thil awm thei tawp nei lo tluk zeta thlunzawm thei hmanraw danglam tak a ni.
pmn01a-subtext: “Ṭhalaite Duh“ Dashboard-ah hian kan lo lawm a che! He interactive tool hian khawvel hmun hrang hranga thalai kum 10-24 inkar atanga kan dawn chhanna leh hriatna te chu hmuh theihin a entir a ni. He hmalakna bulpui ber chu zawhna inhawng tak a ni: “Ka hriselna tihchangtlun nan ka duh...“. Khawvel hmun hrang hrang atanga thalaiten hei hi an chhang a, an mamawh, beiseina leh duhthusam chungchangah hriatna danglam tak min pe a ni. Data te chu chhui la, number hnuaia thawnthu awmte chu hmuchhuak la, khawvel puma thalai tluklehdingawn 1.8 te aw tihchakna kawngah min rawn zawm ve bawk ang che. Campaign chungchang hrechiang duh tan http://www.1point8.org ah hian en theih a ni.
